Personal config files
=====================

* gitconfig / gitignore / gitk
    Git configuration.

* git-prompt.conf
    Git-prompt configuration (Git prompt tool: https://github.com/lvv/git-prompt/).

* tigrc
    tig configuration (Git CLI tool: http://jonas.nitro.dk/tig/).

* bashrc / bash_aliases
    Bash configuration.

* hgrc
    Mercurial configuration.

* taskrc
    taskwarrior configuration (CLI task tool: http://taskwarrior.org/).

* vimrc
    Vim configuraiton.
